snippet.textDisplay:
HEY GUYS ! .... can you have a stuntman discuss the Revenant scene with Leo in a river.
I heard they flipped a (camera) boat then (frantically) hooked to a helicopter line before swimming to shore.
I have heard at least three crazy stories from that film with no video footage. Maybe a stunt guy can give insight.
Even having to seek out warmer waters to match scenes, and randomly finding the cave which is the central starting point of the scene.
It's incredible when you realize it isn't CGI
